title: A.R.S.E.N.A.L. Taste the power
description:
**Works (even sound) with Dosbox under win8**


Arsenal is a C&C style of game, simplistic but with a huge replay-value because of the random map generator. You have access to land- air and sea armies, base defenses etc. The map is also in an infinite loop, as in if you leave on the left side you enter on the right, making it impossible to run into a bottleneck.
